Let $z$ be the image of $-1 - i$ under the dilation.

[asy]
unitsize(0.5 cm);

pair C, P, Q;

C = (2,3);
P = (-1,-1);
Q = interp(C,P,3);
draw((-10,0)--(10,0));
draw((0,-10)--(0,10));
